data.description: Private oasis, tucked away at  the end of Caldwell lane you will find this beautiful 3 BR 2 1/2 bath  stick built, ranch style home. Offering spacious rooms throughout, the  main level includes the living room, dining room, kitchen with island counter &  large pantry.  The elegant primary bedroom offers  2 walk in closets, & luxurious en-suite bath.  In addition, you will find 2 generously sized bedrooms, & main level laundry.  The lower level offers a large storage room, & man-cave/workroom, and a large family room complete with walk out access.  Perfect for entertaining inside and out.  The heating is gas forced air/ heat pump, and central air cooling. Situated on nearly 4 acres, you have plenty of space for outdoor activities , gardening, or just enjoying nature.
